author: Squidmar Miniatures
description:
DONT MISS Porthaven by Archon Studios. Now running on Gamefound. Packed with awesome pirate miniatures in plastic and of course the 70cm long plastic pirate ship:
https://gamefound.com/projects/archon-studio/dnl7-porthaven?refcode=C_mE3fzPzUe1ywQhI1ZLiA

In this weeks video we kitbashed a miniature pirate ship with a ton of Warhammer 40k kits to make the most epic Ork Pirate Ship. And even cooler yet - it's all on a RC body that can drive up to 45 km/h (30 miles per hour). This build is EPIC!
